1. *Gledate* li televiziju? (Do you watch TV?) 
2. Oni *gledaju* u nebo. (They are looking at the sky.)
3. Ona *gleda* u zvezde. (She is looking at the stars.)
4. Mi *gledamo* film. (We are watching a movie.)
5. *Gledali* smo dokumentarac. (We watched a documentary.)
6. Å ta *gledate*? (What are you watching?)
7. On *gleda* u ogledalo. (He is looking in the mirror.)